data.description: This La Cresta charmer is perfect! This home has been cared for and it shows. Featuring 4 bedrooms 2 baths, Located in the mature La Cresta area near the Panorama Bluffs sitting on a corner lot! This home has newer roof, newer windows, newer flooring, modernized bathrooms, AC/Central heating, galley kitchen, indoor utilities. It has so much more to offer outdoors, cute patio area 2 car garage a nice front yard and a side yard you could use for gardening or just for enjoyment.  Book your showing today!
